lead_paragraph: Matt Niskanen and the NHL's top power play unit cashed in yet again as the Washington Capitals outlasted the youthful and overmatched Toronto Maple Leafs 3-2 on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: Capitals Beat Maple Leafs 3-2 Despite Being Outplayed
